WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.216 --> 00:00:02.486
Hello. My name is Maria.

2
00:00:03.042 --> 00:00:05.817
Spacemesh's goal is to create
a cryptocurrency

3
00:00:05.868 --> 00:00:09.301
that will be widely used
as a means of payment

4
00:00:09.447 --> 00:00:14.951
between any two parties in the world
without the possibility of censoring it.

5
00:00:15.300 --> 00:00:18.318
On a technical level,
Spacemesh seeks to solve

6
00:00:18.385 --> 00:00:23.685
integral problems related to
the PoW-based consensus mechanism,

7
00:00:23.752 --> 00:00:29.452
such as centralization, which is inherent
to mining pools and ASIC mining.

8
00:00:29.785 --> 00:00:32.506
Thank you for watching,
and goodbye.

